{"1":[[150,400,"After seven years of struggle, Ethan and I"],[400,588,"are finally getting married."],[746,863,"Ethan."],[930,1000,"Ethan?"],[2164,2406,"Ethan, tell me the truth."],[2506,2644,"Who's gonna better in that wedding dress."],[2644,2786,"Me or your fiancée?"],[2919,2969,"You."],[3069,3203,"God,wish you put that dress on right"],[3203,3378,"now so I could fuck you in it."],[3666,3841,"I want you to remember me forever."],[3899,4058,"Even a month now on your wedding day,"],[4120,4212,"you'll be thinking of what we"],[4212,4316,"did here today."],[4316,4412,"God."],[4471,4842,"You are such an evil little slut."],[4954,5188,"All those business trips, late nights,"],[5259,5463,"excuses so he could meet his lover."],[5463,5597,"I..."],[5597,5805,"I've been such a fool."],[5918,6072,"If you insist on going through with that"],[6072,6260,"wedding, none of us will be there."],[6289,6498,"Take care of yourself, and consider us no"],[6498,6652,"longer your friends."],[6652,6886,"Seven years ago, I cut all ties with my"],[6886,7052,"circle and ran off with Ethan."],[7086,7244,"And Catherine was so pissed she hasn't"],[7244,7386,"spoken to me since then."],[7461,7615,"And now..."],[7615,7820,"all of that for a cheating"],[7820,7962,"jerk like him."],[8108,8229,"I'm calling it off,"],[8229,8333,"don't worry about it."],[9455,9513,"Hey."],[9617,9747,"I messed up,"],[9747,9822,"okay?"],[9847,10076,"Work's been crazy lately,"],[10151,10335,"but that's no excuse for neglecting you."],[10502,10710,"No more late nights, I promise."],[11465,11665,"I always wanted him to use a love song as my"],[11665,11799,"ringtone, but he told me that"],[11799,11916,"it was unprofessional."],[12011,12183,"I guess that only applied to me."],[12566,12904,"I forgot I have some urgent business"],[12983,13071,"at work."],[13204,13296,"I'll come home after"],[13296,13405,"so I don't wake you up."],[13659,13834,"God, I've been so blind."],[13905,14055,"I never doubted him once."],[14109,14314,"Maybe I should just cancel the wedding."]],"2":[[554,700,"Hi, Kate."],[763,842,"It's me."],[900,1084,"Please, please don't hang up."],[1151,1280,"I have decided."],[1393,1501,"I'm leaving Ethan."],[1564,1793,"Yes, I just need some time to wrap things up"],[1793,2027,"first here, but I'm going to do it."],[2081,2185,"Fine."],[2185,2293,"I'll trust you for now."],[2339,2377,"So?"],[2414,2602,"Does this mean that you're going back to"],[2602,2794,"that contract marriage you ran from seven"],[2794,2869,"years ago?"],[3061,3278,"In New York's highly competitive business"],[3278,3495,"world, Alec Moore has long been regarded as"],[3495,3591,"one of the city's most"],[3599,3678,"elite young - That's..."],[3678,3732,"executives. - That's..."],[3749,3832,"Alec Moore."],[3887,4083,"Our families once arranged for the two"],[4083,4283,"of us to be together, but I turned him down"],[4283,4371,"for Ethan."],[4371,4433,"Hello?"],[4517,4625,"Um, yes, I'm here."],[4625,4696,"Um..."],[4792,4879,"Yeah, I'm..."],[4879,4984,"I'm gonna have to accept it."],[4984,5075,"I..."],[5117,5213,"I'm planning to contact the"],[5213,5321,"Moore family, so..."],[5355,5547,"Well, you know, we all thought you"],[5547,5739,"were crazy for turning down Alec,"],[5739,5855,"he must have been super pissed."],[5855,5964,"he must have been super pissed."],[5964,6135,"Last I heard, he's in New York."],[6147,6260,"Maybe for work,"],[6281,6393,"maybe for you."],[6585,6648,"Yeah, okay."],[6715,6769,"I'll talk to you soon."],[6769,6806,"Bye."],[6952,7102,"For me, he's like,"],[7152,7394,"the richest man in the U.S. now."],[7449,7649,"I bet that he showed up just to get back at"],[7649,7778,"me for saying no to him."],[7891,8007,"I can't be here,"],[8007,8174,"I have so many opportunities, and"],[8174,8429,"this really hurts me, but I just don't think"],[8429,8554,"we can be together right now."],[8583,8700,"I'm sorry."],[8929,9125,"God, the last thing I need to do is bump"],[9125,9259,"into him."]],"3":[[0,191,"They say most crushes last three minutes,"],[191,421,"but you're my 181st second."],[421,550,"The moment I knew you were different."],[713,834,"Ethan Lewis."],[1000,1197,"One day before he proposed to me?"],[1297,1514,"Girls, chill on the hate if his fiancé's"],[1514,1655,"cash kept flowing your way."],[1655,1776,"You'd do the same."],[1881,2147,"He actually dared to mess with our shared"],[2147,2210,"assets?"],[2235,2515,"Ethan Lewis, you are so fucked now."],[2515,2794,"I swear I am going to make you pay for this."],[2969,3090,"I will return everything"],[3090,3182,"you ever gave me."],[3182,3470,"The ring, the dress, and then..."],[3574,3645,"you."],[3916,4112,"It is a stunning dress, and I have"],[4112,4291,"really appreciated all the help to find it,"],[4291,4504,"but I just don't think that we're going to"],[4504,4637,"need it anymore, unfortunately."],[4800,4950,"There have been just some..."],[4950,5088,"Hey, sweetheart."],[5188,5347,"Just thought I would pop in"],[5347,5447,"and surprise you."],[5839,6126,"Unbelievable, he actually brought that"],[6126,6214,"woman out here?"],[6256,6318,"Again?"],[6385,6594,"And shoved her in my face?"],[6594,6898,"Hi, I'm Grace Allen, um, Ethan,"],[6898,7048,"Mr. Lewis's intern."],[7257,7624,"I actually thought that Grace here"],[7624,7795,"actually reminds me so much of you"],[7795,7891,"when we first met."],[7907,8099,"So, I thought you two might hit it off."],[8466,8625,"Oh wait, it's lovely,"],[8625,8696,"isn't it?"],[8850,8967,"Do you like it?"],[9046,9117,"I love it."],[9376,9601,"But not many people are as lucky as you"],[9601,9759,"getting to marry the person you love."],[9818,10035,"Why don't you have her go try it on?"],[10197,10431,"I mean, it's bad luck to see the bride in"],[10464,10648,"the dress before the wedding, so..."],[10714,10814,"it only makes sense."],[11031,11102,"Go ahead."],[11102,11182,"Yeah, yeah."],[11440,11565,"What, you're not going to go with?"],[11682,11924,"I thought that you'd be so eager to assist."],[11991,12157,"Did she catch on?"],[12157,12308,"No, no, can't be."],[12308,12441,"She loves me."],[12441,12612,"She's just jealous I showed up"],[12612,12683,"with someone else."],[12883,12946,"What's that mean?"],[13038,13083,"Nothing."],[13605,13651,"Oh."],[13742,13947,"Oh, how pretty."],[14268,14397,"You look like you could get married"],[14397,14456,"right here."],[15031,15098,"What-"],[15632,15694,"Maria!"],[15882,15932,"What?"],[15982,16111,"The dress was tainted long before"],[16111,16182,"I stained it."],[16237,16337,"How dare you think that"],[16337,16441,"I'd put that back on."],[16679,16787,"Maria!"]],"4":[[12,125,"Maria, come on!"],[179,275,"Are you done"],[275,421,"with this little temper tantrum?"],[513,567,"Come home."],[608,717,"We clearly need to talk."],[1084,1142,"What else"],[1142,1255,"did she leave in your car, huh?"],[1343,1426,"Her panties?"],[1463,1651,"Okay, this ends now."],[1701,1889,"Our wedding is coming up so soon, and we"],[1889,2031,"already have so much to deal with."],[2031,2139,"And that is why - Don't let that..."],[2139,2214,"I said,"],[2214,2364,"let's just cancel it."],[2364,2544,"Can you stop being jealous?"],[2544,2756,"How will our company continue to grow if"],[2756,2886,"you crash out over"],[2886,3040,"every girl I work with?"],[3290,3349,"Come on."],[3632,3795,"You know you can't live without me."],[3908,4095,"That reminds me, I'm gonna have to take"],[4095,4270,"back what's mine before I leave."],[4462,4525,"And,"],[4562,4733,"with your grandmother in the ICU,"],[4850,5042,"it's her last wish for you to get married,"],[5080,5176,"isn't it?"],[5301,5401,"Come on, when's the last time"],[5401,5484,"you visited her?"],[5522,5593,"Amanda and I are"],[5593,5730,"the only family you have left."],[5755,5989,"How dare you bring up my grandma"],[5989,6093,"to threaten me!"],[6093,6306,"You don't even get to mention her!"],[6306,6410,"Just, duh!"],[6410,6514,"Leave me alone!"],[6535,6614,"Maria, come on!"],[6614,6681,"No!"],[7303,7353,"Fuck."],[9255,9338,"Damn it!"],[11978,12070,"Alec."]],"5":[[70,141,"Alec."],[216,312,"Long time no see."],[508,750,"You know, there's better ways of getting"],[750,896,"my attention than hitting my car,"],[896,975,"Miss Carter."],[975,1042,"You..."],[1042,1192,"you didn't go on the green light, and"],[1217,1334,"that's why I hit you."],[1497,1559,"Damn."],[1601,1776,"He definitely found me on purpose"],[1776,1876,"to make me pay for"],[1876,2006,"rejecting our engagement."],[2990,3057,"There."],[3111,3328,"Now you can contact me anytime you want."],[3620,3807,"With your grandmother in the ICU,"],[3845,4024,"it's her last wish for you to get married,"],[4062,4129,"isn't it?"],[4237,4429,"He was my contract lover anyway,"],[4429,4571,"so why not just ask him"],[4571,4658,"if he wants to marry me?"],[4658,4725,"If not,"],[4758,4850,"I'll just move on."],[4929,5034,"Alec Moore,"],[5117,5201,"I want to marry you."],[5417,5568,"And I'm giving you seven seconds."],[5568,5663,"If you don't say anything,"],[5663,5776,"then that means yes."],[6005,6060,"One."],[6218,6268,"Two."],[6435,6481,"Three."],[6673,6727,"Four."],[7190,7253,"Seven."],[8083,8170,"So,"],[8254,8341,"is that a yes?"],[8404,8495,"Well, that depends."],[8612,8767,"Are you gonna play me again and elope with"],[8767,8925,"another man like you did last time?"],[8954,9067,"Of course..."],[9134,9200,"not!"],[9246,9401,"I mean, how could I?"],[9401,9467,"I just..."],[9542,9622,"There are a few things"],[9622,9713,"that I need to take care of,"],[9713,9872,"and no longer than a month."],[9905,9959,"Do you think"],[9959,10076,"that you could just wait for me?"],[11511,11674,"I waited for seven years."],[11699,11815,"What's one more month?"]],"6":[[508,596,"Grandma,"],[746,871,"you're the only family"],[871,1017,"that I have left now."],[1172,1401,"What's wrong, my sweetheart?"],[1459,1797,"A beautiful bride can never cry."],[1901,2127,"Did Ethan not come with you?"],[2210,2364,"No, no, um..."],[2419,2665,"He didn't, but I'm fine."],[2756,2857,"I am."],[2948,3178,"If Grandma knew Ethan had been lying to me"],[3178,3294,"all these years..."],[3357,3524,"would she still blessed my marriage?"],[3691,3978,"If only I could place that necklace on you"],[4024,4195,"like I did for your mother."],[4220,4562,"You are going to be the most beautiful"],[4562,4729,"bride in the world."],[4867,5209,"It's just such a pity."],[6418,6619,"Tomorrow, 1 p.m. Sterling Auction."],[6644,6785,"You will find what you're looking for."],[6881,6981,"What do you mean?"],[7132,7361,"319 Maple Lane."],[8149,8320,"Sir, Ms. Carter's evening gown"],[8320,8416,"has arrived."],[8416,8512,"Would you like me to"],[8512,8616,"confirm her attendance?"],[8800,8896,"Leave me alone!"],[9067,9196,"No, no."],[9275,9509,"Let her have her little hissy fit."],[9743,9793,"You."],[9864,9968,"Put on the dress."],[10005,10097,"You’re coming with me."],[10181,10322,"Maria needs to regret"],[10322,10468,"losing her temper with me."],[10514,10677,"That'll teach her a lesson."],[12341,12470,"I can't believe that I ran into"],[12470,12625,"these two riffraffs here."],[12658,12800,"And daring to wear my dress?"],[12850,13017,"Absolutely infuriating."],[13129,13367,"Bro, you are living the dream!"],[13388,13551,"Wedding next month with your fiancée,"],[13551,13776,"and this little bit of honey by your side?"],[13947,14059,"You finally did it, bro."],[14118,14226,"I mean, look at Maria."],[14226,14356,"She's so in love with him,"],[14356,14522,"she can't let you go anymore."],[14564,14735,"She really got you by the peep."]],"7":[[0,129,"Maria actually"],[129,271,"followed me to the auction."],[316,383,"I knew her"],[383,525,"silly tantrum would blow over."],[900,950,"So,"],[1017,1213,"you actually followed me here."],[1213,1459,"You know, that is the exact attitude I need"],[1459,1597,"if you want me to forgive you."],[1851,1956,"Does anybody hear..."],[2039,2143,"barking?"],[3199,3265,"Oh."],[3386,3536,"So that's what you're after."],[3574,3703,"You should have told me earlier."],[3824,3883,"You know what?"],[3962,4137,"Why don't you beg?"],[4204,4287,"Right now."],[4354,4483,"And I'll maybe buy it for you."],[4742,4867,"I don't even need you."],[5034,5242,"Without me buying it, nobody else would."],[5413,5568,"I can buy it myself."],[5626,5843,"And if you have any shred of manners left,"],[5876,5993,"you'd step aside."],[7824,7937,"Ladies and gentlemen,"],[7937,8208,"welcome to Sterling Galleries."],[8208,8408,"We are about to begin the auction,"],[8408,8495,"and first up"],[8495,8775,"is the illustrious Buchanan necklace"],[8775,8942,"that has bedazzled ballrooms"],[8942,9042,"for centuries."],[9088,9184,"Yes, that's my grandma's"],[9184,9292,"wedding necklace."],[9321,9505,"She lost it ages ago, and it's always been"],[9505,9622,"her biggest regret."],[9684,9788,"She likes that,"],[9818,9884,"huh?"],[9918,10022,"I'm not going to let her have it"],[10022,10105,"that easily."],[10197,10377,"Do I hear an opening bid?"],[10447,10589,"One hundred and fifty thousand."],[10643,10806,"One hundred and fifty thousand."],[10839,10910,"Five hundred."],[11190,11382,"No matter how high she wants to go,"],[11448,11569,"I'm going to outbid her."],[11674,11924,"One million dollars."],[11924,12011,"Ten million!"],[12216,12449,"Ten million dollars!"],[12449,12583,"That is way beyond"],[12583,12750,"the necklace's actual value."],[12804,12971,"Looks like Ethan will do anything just to"],[12971,13075,"spite me."],[13100,13217,"I don't even have enough to"],[13217,13334,"fight for it anymore."],[13388,13592,"Ethan, is that for me?"],[13655,13784,"I love it so much."],[13838,13913,"Thank you."],[13963,14172,"Uh, yeah."],[14218,14322,"Yeah, of course."],[14322,14422,"It's for you."],[14727,14827,"Beg me."],[15202,15498,"Eleven million dollars."],[15828,15920,"Fifteen million."],[16374,16491,"Has he lost his mind?"],[16491,16674,"Fifteen million dollars!"],[16712,16933,"I guess I'm failing everything now."],[16958,17108,"Going once!"],[17154,17288,"Grandma, I'm sorry."],[17325,17479,"Going twice!"],[17867,17955,"Thirty million."],[19886,20082,"I said thirty million dollars."]],"8":[[29,179,"Bruh, that's Alec Moore."],[221,379,"Richest family in the US."],[429,529,"We're not messing with him."],[600,734,"Alec Moore?"],[734,809,"Damn it."],[834,1017,"His power and wealth could crush me."],[1063,1184,"I can't piss him off."],[1234,1409,"Sold to Mr. Moore"],[1409,1647,"for thirty million dollars."],[1710,1889,"Why would Alec bid on a necklace that's"],[1889,2035,"completely useless to him?"],[2064,2373,"The necklace is worth maybe ten grand tops."],[2481,2711,"Tomorrow, 1 p.m. Sterling Auction."],[2711,2873,"You will find what you're looking for."],[3282,3457,"Maybe he's just still finding new ways to"],[3457,3599,"punish me?"],[3866,3974,"Mr. Moore,"],[4037,4208,"I had no idea you wanted that"],[4208,4304,"necklace as well."],[4358,4483,"As soon as you started bidding,"],[4483,4600,"I backed off."],[4600,4829,"I would never dare to compete with you."],[4992,5100,"That's what you chose?"],[5334,5513,"He's clearly mocking me for breaking off"],[5513,5593,"the engagement,"],[5593,5776,"but now that he owns that necklace,"],[5834,6010,"how could I even ask him for anything?"],[6139,6197,"Choose what?"],[6197,6272,"What do you mean?"],[8391,8495,"I believe this necklace"],[8495,8587,"is meant for you."]],"9":[[145,467,"Seven years ago, I chose Ethan over Alec."],[467,809,"And now, Ethan has no shame in parading his"],[809,1172,"mistress while Alec gives me what I want."],[1355,1468,"It's beautiful."],[1505,1643,"You know, next time you should give me a"],[1643,1793,"better man to compete against."],[1951,2114,"Because it looks like I crushed him."],[2635,2752,"How could you messing around"],[2752,2844,"with another man?"],[3007,3203,"That is rich coming from you."],[3257,3349,"What?"],[3787,3962,"Thank you, Alec."],[4500,4579,"Out of my way."],[4704,4954,"And out of my life forever."],[5025,5109,"Maria!"],[5534,5622,"Grandma."],[5672,5935,"I finally got back what belongs to you."],[5989,6193,"I can't wait to give it to you."],[6456,6710,"Why the hell would Alec Moore help her?"],[6756,6977,"What exactly is going on between them?"],[7065,7228,"Are you still thinking about Miss Carter?"],[7636,7724,"Ethan, you promised that"],[7724,7845,"you'd give me an answer."],[7895,8028,"Okay, I'm almost three months pregnant."],[8028,8229,"I won't be able to hide it much longer."],[8329,8445,"Will you accept me"],[8550,8650,"and the baby?"],[8742,8888,"I can accept the child"],[8950,9125,"on one condition."],[9246,9601,"Maria must never know you're pregnant."],[10418,10556,"Dr. Henry,"],[10556,10656,"what a coincidence."],[10656,10823,"I'm actually on my way to the hospital"],[10823,10906,"right now."],[10906,11015,"Ms. Carter,"],[11015,11131,"your grandma has suddenly"],[11131,11223,"stopped breathing."],[11223,11353,"She's being resuscitated."],[11353,11478,"Please come immediately."],[11494,11569,"What?"],[11632,11686,"Doctor..."]],"10":[[246,316,"Help her!"],[763,871,"Your grandma has suddenly"],[871,955,"stopped breathing."],[955,1117,"She's being resuscitated."],[1301,1384,"Help her!"],[1384,1459,"Ethan."],[1484,1559,"Help her!"],[1589,1664,"Ethan."],[1826,1918,"Help her!"],[2185,2264,"Help her!"],[2293,2373,"Help her!"],[2923,3065,"We don't have enough hands."],[3065,3186,"We need to triage."],[3883,3970,"Help her!"],[3970,4091,"She's carrying my child."],[4204,4354,"She's carrying my child."],[5059,5155,"I'm sorry."],[5209,5376,"We were unable to save her."],[5422,5530,"Your grandma..."],[5563,5655,"she just passed."],[5880,6076,"Ethan Lewis, because of you, I missed my"],[6076,6256,"grandma's last moments."],[6256,6393,"And when I needed you,"],[6393,6552,"you were saving your mistress,"],[6552,6719,"who's carrying your child!"],[8087,8283,"Canceling the wedding would be too merciful"],[8283,8391,"for you."],[8429,8804,"No, instead, I will ruin you at it."],[8846,8975,"At my wedding,"],[8975,9125,"you will pay for betraying me,"],[9125,9296,"and I will tear your world apart."],[9296,9467,"Total humiliation."],[9592,9738,"Somebody help me..."],[11970,12062,"Alec,"],[12195,12424,"it's you."]],"11":[[58,312,"Alec, it's you."],[392,554,"Maria."],[959,1051,"Maria."],[1205,1288,"Maria, look at me."],[1343,1413,"Look at me."],[1488,1576,"It's gonna be all right."],[3607,3712,"Where are we?"],[3757,3891,"You're in my family's private medical suite"],[3891,4029,"at Moore Medical."],[4187,4312,"Thank you."],[4400,4587,"So, Ms. Carter, is this what you call"],[4587,4738,"making it big and having lackeys all"],[4738,4946,"over Los Angeles when you turn me down?"],[5004,5334,"I was wrong to throw that in your face"],[5334,5488,"all of those years ago."],[6835,6986,"Beautiful."],[7198,7582,"Yeah, thank you for buying it and,"],[7582,7766,"and for giving it to me."],[7766,7974,"It really means so much."],[8045,8183,"Consider it an engagement gift."],[8350,8604,"So you really want to marry me?"],[8750,8933,"And not just to get back at me for ruining"],[8933,9063,"our engagement?"],[9738,9880,"Of course I'll marry you."],[10239,10322,"But,"],[10352,10485,"if we were supposed to be"],[10485,10639,"married, then there would be some"],[10639,10785,"clear-cut sign."],[10885,10969,"Well..."],[11461,11603,"Well, I guess that's a pretty clear-cut sign"],[11603,11695,"right there."],[13909,14068,"It's not exactly the way I planned"],[14068,14151,"the proposal,"],[14180,14339,"but I want to make things clear."],[14476,14593,"You belong to me now."]],"12":[[617,729,"Where are you?"],[729,875,"Stop being so ridiculous."],[875,1009,"Keep playing these games"],[1009,1130,"before our wedding."],[1130,1234,"Answer me!"],[1401,1614,"Everything I own is tied up with him all"],[1614,1685,"of these years."],[1685,1860,"All my shares, every cent"],[1860,2001,"in my bank accounts."],[2001,2189,"I need to regain control of my assets"],[2189,2402,"and sever all financial ties with"],[2402,2756,"him before I ruin him."],[2902,3040,"You ready to get out of here?"],[3132,3219,"Yeah."],[3653,3803,"Hey, I think that if it's a girl, then we"],[3803,3937,"should name her Allison."],[3937,4041,"Listen, Grace,"],[4099,4254,"I will take responsibility"],[4254,4416,"for this child, but it's not going to"],[4416,4583,"change my marriage with Maria."],[4671,4713,"But..."],[4713,4892,"Maria's not going to accept a betrayal"],[4892,4988,"like this."],[5034,5242,"She can't know about us."],[5305,5551,"And you can never talk to her face to face,"],[5551,5626,"got it?"],[5976,6089,"Where are you?"],[6089,6310,"You're running out my patience."],[6735,6856,"Wait, is that Maria?"],[7461,7549,"Ethan!"],[10009,10080,"Ethan!"],[10118,10193,"Ethan!"],[10193,10306,"Hey, you need to see this."],[10306,10381,"Hold it!"],[10381,10452,"What!"],[11265,11340,"No, no, no."],[11465,11532,"Oh no!"],[11686,11803,"No fucking way!"],[11845,11941,"Maria."],[12141,12278,"She really left me."]],"13":[[663,930,"Ms. Carter, we just received the"],[930,1121,"replacement photo for the reception, and I"],[1121,1388,"just wanted to confirm you agreed"],[1388,1463,"to the change."],[1463,1497,"Okay."],[2410,2615,"Yes, I accept the change."],[2615,2752,"Are you sure?"],[2752,2811,"It's not..."],[2811,2927,"Replace it."],[2927,3032,"Grace wants her wedding?"],[3086,3148,"Good."],[3199,3278,"She'll get it."],[3328,3532,"And I will make it very..."],[3532,3645,"very interesting."],[3695,3912,"And Ethan will lose everything that he"],[3912,4158,"owns in the most humiliating way"],[4158,4241,"imaginable."],[4291,4366,"Everything okay?"],[4475,4654,"I know you must think that I am a fool."],[4721,4975,"I mean, seven years of love and trust just"],[5059,5180,"thrown away like trash."],[5580,5684,"Well, you have me now."],[5764,5847,"I'll let you choose."],[6856,6940,"Ethan."],[7282,7453,"Damn it, Maria, the wedding's in less than"],[7453,7532,"three weeks."],[7570,7782,"Gossip sites are already on fire about"],[7782,7928,"you running off with another man."],[7941,8037,"What's your problem?"],[8162,8329,"What is he talking about?"],[8329,8483,"My assistant must have leaked it"],[8483,8571,"something."],[8583,8812,"Until I've got all the proof and all my"],[8812,9088,"assets back, I need Ethan to believe that"],[9088,9200,"we're still getting married."],[9271,9576,"It's probably just some bored reporters"],[9576,9763,"trying to spread rumors for likes and"],[9763,9822,"follows."],[9855,10168,"That is it, so nothing to worry about, okay?"],[10218,10385,"Maria, those rumors could ruin our"],[10385,10531,"company's chances of going public."],[10614,10848,"I'm just warning you, watch yourself."],[10994,11236,"Can't believe that coming from a serial"],[11236,11286,"cheater."],[11323,11540,"I'm going to call back every cent that he's"],[11540,11715,"taken from me over these past seven"],[11715,11928,"years, and then I'm going to give him a"],[11928,12137,"wedding he will never forget."],[12241,12404,"She's only marrying me for the family"],[12404,12504,"contracts."],[12504,12700,"She still loves him, even after all his"],[12700,12762,"betrayal."],[12791,12962,"I'm hopelessly devoted, and yet I"],[12967,13121,"wish she'd just turn her heart away."]],"14":[[20,183,"The second trimester is going well."],[216,400,"We have 10% revenue this year."],[1322,1555,"Oh my goodness, Ms. Allen, is your foot"],[1555,1601,"okay?"],[1601,1705,"Yeah, yeah, I'm fine."],[1705,1897,"Oh, so glad to hear it."],[1897,2106,"I thought that you were having a foot"],[2106,2356,"cramp or something, and wanted"],[2356,2552,"Mr. Lewis to massage it for you."],[2769,2827,"Maria."],[2869,2932,"What?"],[2973,3207,"You don't want to massage her foot?"],[3424,3670,"We are clearly in a meeting right now."],[3670,3774,"Can you go wait in my office?"],[3874,3949,"I can't."],[4012,4195,"You see, someone changed the lock."],[4250,4504,"It's pretty funny because, if I remember"],[4504,4729,"correctly, I founded this company."],[4733,5042,"I am also the vice president, so..."],[5163,5376,"remind me again, why wasn't I invited to"],[5376,5430,"this meeting?"],[5551,5609,"Nobody?"],[5784,6010,"Everyone here should remember to keep the"],[6010,6202,"company's best interest in mind."],[6247,6589,"That means knowing who to challenge, and"],[6589,6756,"knowing who to adore."],[7065,7244,"All right, meeting's adjourned."],[7319,7365,"You can go."],[7620,7695,"Thank you all."],[7770,7870,"Have a good day."],[8333,8466,"I'll go get Ms. Carter some coffee."],[8533,8662,"That's such a great idea."],[8662,8758,"Thank you, Ms. Allen."],[9121,9363,"So, you want to tell me why interns are"],[9363,9563,"allowed at senior staff meetings?"],[9684,9893,"You've gotten so generous."],[9943,10064,"I already told you."],[10072,10297,"She reminds me of you when you were younger."],[10322,10539,"I'm sorry for trying to give her a job"],[10548,10610,"opportunity."],[10673,10706,"But fine."],[10769,10894,"If you don't want her to work here, I'll"],[10894,10931,"fire her."],[10960,11027,"Really?"]],"15":[[312,383,"Fire her."],[412,554,"She can't even bring us coffee without"],[554,608,"messing it up."],[717,800,"Can't do it?"],[1117,1201,"I'm sorry, Miss Carter."],[1201,1338,"I'll clean it up right now, okay?"],[1976,2189,"Damn it, Maria, stop being so hysterical,"],[2189,2239,"okay?"],[2439,2594,"You have clearly forgotten that I have"],[2594,2740,"access to the security cameras."],[2765,2923,"You really want everyone seeing what"],[2923,3094,"you two get up to after hours?"],[3140,3244,"I don't know what you're talking about."],[3407,3536,"No, I can't lose Ethan."],[3536,3666,"If I do, I'll have nothing left."],[3699,3924,"It's my fault, Miss Carter, okay?"],[4033,4129,"I just, I was..."],[4212,4325,"I'm in love with Ethan, and"],[4325,4362,"I'm pregn-"],[4537,4583,"Enough."],[4708,4808,"I am"],[4808,4909,"Fine, fine."],[4984,5176,"If you really want her gone, I'm sorry"],[5176,5313,"Miss Allen, but I have to let you go."],[5359,5413,"Now!"],[5501,5576,"There, satisfied?"],[5693,5768,"What?"],[5784,5843,"No."],[5910,6056,"Ms. Carter please, okay?"],[6056,6206,"I, I, I have student loans"],[6206,6293,"that I have to pay off."],[6293,6368,"Please, okay?"],[6368,6460,"I need to stay here."],[6502,6614,"Just let me stay, okay?"],[6673,6931,"But you can't do the work anyway, can you?"],[6986,7240,"You said it yourself, you're pregnant?"]],"16":[[0,191,"No, that's not what I..."],[266,417,"No, no, that's not..."],[462,704,"Did she catch on?"],[804,942,"No, no, can't be."],[996,1101,"She loves me."],[1155,1280,"She's just jealous I showed up with"],[1280,1347,"someone else."],[1418,1455,"Pressed."],[1547,1805,"She said she was pressed."],[1822,2047,"I mean, it's clearly so stressful"],[2047,2110,"working here,"],[2173,2344,"so I think it's time that she takes"],[2348,2406,"a break."],[2573,2752,"Now is not a good time to tip them off."],[2765,2961,"Not before I walk away with every penny"],[2961,3086,"that he's stolen from me."],[3111,3486,"Maria, how about I cancel all of my"],[3490,3732,"meetings and take you to lunch,"],[3745,3787,"okay?"],[3908,3933,"Fine."],[4946,5004,"Um..."],[5071,5134,"this?"],[5334,5417,"Sexy Matte."],[5980,6056,"What are you doing?"],[6193,6289,"Hey, what are you doing with that?"],[6314,6468,"Oh, you know, just"],[6519,6669,"redecorating the office."],[7023,7232,"No, no, no, no, no, no, not that."]],"17":[[746,859,"Our engagement photo,"],[859,1017,"Maria treasures so much."],[1059,1142,"And now,"],[1142,1309,"she just throws it away,"],[1322,1401,"like trash."],[1476,1534,"Damn it!"],[1897,1993,"Quit hassling me."],[1993,2097,"I'm busy right now."],[2122,2173,"Ethan,"],[2202,2264,"you have to help me."],[2264,2377,"I got so dizzy,"],[2377,2419,"and I fell."],[2423,2494,"I'm scared about"],[2494,2569,"our baby."],[3107,3278,"I have some"],[3336,3461,"urgent client business"],[3461,3541,"t