w up."],[4241,4350,"So today,"],[4429,4763,"I'm gonna give you ninety-nine lashes."],[4775,4904,"And pretty soon,"],[5055,5138,"you'll be nothing but"],[5138,5301,"a stain on this floor."],[5313,5392,"No, don't do this."],[5392,5492,"Steve, don't do this."]],"40":[[0,133,"Steve, please don't do this."],[133,208,"Please, ah-"],[362,479,"That's one!"],[667,784,"Steve, please."],[796,863,"Now, I get it."],[1009,1146,"Where is my fiancée?"],[1167,1430,"She really left E.M. Group to work for you?"],[1480,1551,"I'll call you back."],[1906,2018,"Your fiancée isn't here."],[2077,2193,"Only my personal assistant."],[2348,2414,"Listen,"],[2423,2640,"Moore Enterprises doesn't give you"],[2648,2952,"permission to snatch up my future wife."],[2977,3098,"You know she only came here"],[3098,3194,"to piss me off,"],[3219,3269,"right?"],[3365,3520,"Well, I'm quitting on her behalf."],[3620,3791,"You see, I've known Maria a long, long"],[3791,3837,"time."],[3987,4129,"She would never let a man speak on her"],[4129,4200,"behalf."],[4245,4471,"You don't know shit about her,"],[4483,4671,"and you better stay away from her."],[4763,4963,"I'm marrying her next week."],[5013,5105,"Mr. Moore."],[5342,5467,"There's a problem with Ms. Carter."],[5472,5580,"What is it? -Where is she?"],[5651,5718,"She's missing."],[5784,5922,"Just a few hours ago, she asked me to call"],[5922,6051,"Steve back here,"],[6089,6197,"and now they both vanished."],[6197,6335,"She's not answering her phone, either."],[6452,6527,"We'll find her."],[6556,6598,"Now."],[7102,7157,"Come on Maria."],[7157,7265,"Pick up. Pick up. Pick up."],[7444,7574,"Let all the managers know that if they"],[7574,7728,"don't find Maria in the next five minutes,"],[7728,7778,"they're all fired."],[7820,7945,"Sure, boss, but"],[7945,8087,"what reason should I give them?"],[8124,8224,"Don't give them a reason."],[8249,8425,"Maria's my responsibility."],[8425,8529,"Get her done."]],"41":[[8,133,"Please don't do this."],[342,429,"Ninety-eight."],[759,846,"Ninety-nine."],[1238,1322,"Well,"],[1372,1559,"let me tell you something, whore."],[1701,1830,"Over the years, I've made quite a bit of"],[1830,1989,"money from this branch."],[2022,2139,"Though,should we say,"],[2202,2314,"good investments?"],[2419,2573,"I should have known that it was you,"],[2573,2694,"you scumbag."],[2765,2952,"Mr. Moore is never gonna forgive you."],[3023,3182,"Actually, I hear Alec Moore is getting"],[3182,3311,"married soon, so"],[3382,3507,"why don't you become mine?"],[3524,3649,"No, no, get away from me,"],[3649,3712,"get out!"],[4237,4295,"Yeah."],[4587,4646,"Is it done?"],[4667,4788,"Get your ass back here."],[4842,4996,"Moore's turning the whole company upside"],[5000,5121,"down trying to find Maria."],[5159,5217,"Wait, what?"],[5234,5351,"Quit wasting time."],[5388,5488,"If that bitch doesn't show up"],[5488,5618,"in five minutes,"],[5643,5818,"he's firing everyone."],[5851,6018,"Make her disappear before anyone can"],[6018,6076,"find her."],[6368,6464,"What the fuck?"],[7044,7115,"Steve Rich,"],[7115,7236,"where the fuck are you right now?"],[7332,7478,"I had no idea."],[7478,7565,"Where is she?"],[7578,7716,"Where's my fiancée?"],[7716,7811,"I know"],[7811,7882,"you know something."],[7882,7982,"I see it all over that"],[7982,8166,"ugly little face of yours."]],"42":[[371,608,"Mr. Moore, are you out of your mind?"],[621,700,"My brother and I"],[700,892,"have been loyal to Moore enterprises."],[959,1088,"How can you treat us like this?"],[1096,1263,"Are they talking about the new girl?"],[1292,1359,"I guess the big boss"],[1359,1539,"has something going on with her."],[1618,1701,"You don't trust us."],[1764,2031,"You sent a complete stranger to spy on us,"],[2110,2256,"and now you want to fire us?"],[2323,2435,"All because she ran off on you."],[2502,2594,"Hey, boss,"],[2619,2736,"you've always made it clear"],[2736,2848,"that you treat all of your"],[2848,2961,"employees with respect."],[3015,3111,"But this?"],[3123,3253